title: Rachel Gardner - Senior Paid Media Executive - Torchbox

metadata.description: Rachel helps our clients to achieve their strategic goals through paid media, ensuring ads get in front of the right people, whether that's potential donors, prospective volunteers, eager fundraisers or people interested in their research.
